# ============================================================
#  .gitignore — VFM-Registration-MasterThesis (PUBLIC repo)
#  Default-deny for anything that could carry patient imagery,
#  model weights, or bulky third-party clones.
# ============================================================

# ---- Patient medical data — NEVER commit (public repo) ----
data/
code/gui/02_view_results/
code/gui/04_samples/
code/registration/000010_femur.png
# any stray clinical raster anywhere
*.tif
*.tiff
*.dcm
*.dicom

# ---- Model weights / checkpoints (too large; not source) ----
checkpoints/
code/gui/03_tool/weights/
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.safetensors
*.onnx

# ---- Third-party clones (obtain from upstream; see README) ----
# sam2_lib (SAM2 / MedSAM2 framework) IS included as code; only its weights
# (checkpoints/, *.pt) and demo media are excluded (see below).
code/gui/03_tool/sam3_code/
code/registration/dupla_renderers/

# ---- sam2_lib: drop non-code bulk, keep library + training source ----
code/sam2_lib/demo/
code/sam2_lib/notebooks/
code/sam2_lib/sav_dataset/
code/sam2_lib/SAM_2.egg-info/
*.mp4
*.avi
*.mov

# ---- Python / OS cruft ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.DS_Store
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.zip
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/

# ---- results/: default-deny, allowlist only non-patient figures ----
results/*
!results/fig_pipeline.png
!results/fig_dual_plane_geometry.png
!results/fig_r1_cdf.png
!results/fig_r3_robustness.png
!results/fig_e3_clicks.png
!results/fig_gs_pipeline.png
!results/fig_gs_pose_error.png
!results/fig_gs_overlay.png

# temp-moved nested git history (restored after commit)
**/.git__BAK/

# proposal docx may embed patient figures — excluded from public repo
docs/Proposal.docx

# doc + thesis (paper) — code-only repo per user (2026-05-26)
docs/
chapters/
references.bib
thesis_framework.md
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
